He is gonna be a tough enemy for Luffy later on. Not just based on the Dark-Dark Fruit, but the fact he's got other powers going for him is why Teech will not be an easy enemy.

BTW, nice idea on the Pen-Pen Fruit. I had one for a guy in the Marines/Navy for the One Piece RP my pal Kurt and I are working on; it's called the Ground-Ground Fruit, a Logia-Type which allows the person who has its powers, Turks Sol, the leader of a black ops unit called the Black Clouds, to control the earth itself and make parts of his body into earth. Like the Sand-Sand Fruit however, liquids are a weakness for him besides the general fact of all Devil Fruit weaknesses.
